    <item>
      <title>可是七十年代的东南亚也不安全啊！</title>
      <link>https://jimmysong.io/blog/the-serpent-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 May 2025 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
      <author>Jimmy Song</author>
      <guid>https://jimmysong.io/blog/the-serpent-review/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
